<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURES 15–18" captionStartId="10.[151,264,1510,1534]" captionTargetBox="[169,1311,186,1480]" captionTargetId="figure-23@10.[156,1432,181,1486]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 15–18. Xanthopygus luctuosus (Blanchard). 15. Habitus photograph. 16. Pronotum. 17. Sternites 6–8. 18. Antenna. Not to scale." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6048493" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6048493/files/figure.png" pageId="25" pageNumber="176">Fig. 17</figureCitation>
)................................................................................................ 2
