<figureCitation box="[788,904,1209,1231]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–26" captionStartId="12.[151,264,1956,1980]" captionTargetBox="[214,1366,665,1930]" captionTargetId="figure-148@12.[214,1373,658,1932]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURES 23–26. Xanthopygus major (Bernhauer). 23. Habitus photograph. 24. Pronotum. 25. Sternites 6–8. 26. Antenna. Not to scale." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6048501" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6048501/files/figure.png" pageId="25" pageNumber="176">Figs. 23–24</figureCitation>
